    "title": "Resistance: State and Memory",
    "explanation": "L'état a un but. Le souvenir est là. On ne va pas abandonner. — notice the negated future: ne va pas + [verb] = will NOT do.\n\nCompare: On abandonne (we abandon — present) vs. On ne va pas abandonner (we will NOT abandon — negated future). The refusal points forward.\n\nRe-read and find every negation. What is being refused or denied?"
